{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1570e530ea","title":"毛泽东关于打招呼会议的两个批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"99aff01172","index":0,"year":1975,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"1570e530ea"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1fafa52fa3","type":"title","text":"关于打招呼会议的两个批语","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1570e530ea"},{"id":"862d02bd7e","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1570e530ea"},{"id":"c10118bc9d","type":"paragraph","text":"很好。但不仅只是老同志，要有中年、青年各一人同听同议，如同此次十七人会议那样。即也要对青年人打招呼，否则青年人也会犯错误。请政治局再议一次，或者分两次开，或者先分后合。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1570e530ea"},{"id":"6ac7c58887","type":"appellation","text":"小平同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1570e530ea"},{"id":"d9740560d0","type":"paragraph","text":"还是你们议的好，先给老同志打招呼。青年问题暂缓。因有的还未结合，有的在打派仗（如七机部），有的貌合神离（如清华），召集不起来。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1570e530ea"}],"page":{"id":"29ac1b0088","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1570e530ea","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}